::Prowl::

Prowl frowns as Iron Raptor takes his hands off her, wondering if she 
was still upset about the truck comment untill he heard her say 
something about Dinobot. He takes off at a run after her as she
leaves 
the CR chambers, reaching Dinobot a few seconds after her.

He swears as he looks at the Maximal, running up to his other side to 
assist Iron Raptor in getting him to the CR room.

"What happened to him?" he asks, looking back at the trail of 
mech-fluid in the halls.
